---
title: One-Pot Chorizo, Chicken & Creamy Tomato Fusilli with Leek & Parmesan Cheese
description: Cheesy, rich and red, it’s a tomato sauce that’s very easy on the tastebuds. There’s tomato and leek stirred through alongside mild chorizo and chicken, toss everything in a bowl of fusilli pasta and dinner just became irresistible.
